                              POETRY
               CREATIVE COMPUTING  MORRISTOWN, NEW JERSEY



MIDNIGHT DREARY THING OF EVIL THRILLED ME,
QUOTH THE RAVEN SLOWLY CREEPING 
BIRD OR FIEND THRILLED ME, QUOTH THE RAVEN
     NEVERMORE 
BIRD OR FIEND
     NEVER FLITTING QUOTH THE RAVEN ...EVERMORE 
PROPHET
     NEVER FLITTING, SIGN OF PARTING ...EVERMORE 
FIERY EYES, BURNED SIGN OF PARTING YET AGAIN 

THRILLED ME
MIDNIGHT DREARY THRILLED ME SHALL BE LIFTED ...EVERMORE

MIDNIGHT DREARY
     NEVER FLITTING
 YET AGAIN 
PROPHET
     THRILLED ME SHALL BE LIFTED NOTHING MORE

BIRD OR FIEND
     NEVER FLITTING
QUOTH THE RAVEN YET AGAIN 
FIERY EYES, BEGUILING ME
DARKNESS THERE NEVERMORE 

NEVER FLITTING BIRD OR FIEND, BURNED
SHALL BE LIFTED
     SLOWLY CREEPING 
BIRD OR FIEND
     BEGUILING ME QUOTH THE RAVEN,
     ...EVERMORE 
FIERY EYES BURNED SIGN OF PARTING NEVERMORE, 
FIERY EYES NEVER FLITTING SHALL BE LIFTED
     ...EVERMORE

FIERY EYES STILL SITTING.... SIGN OF PARTING NEVERMORE 

BURNED
PROPHET
     THRILLED ME AND MY SOUL NEVERMORE

THING OF EVIL
     NEVER FLITTING,
SHALL BE LIFTED ...EVERMORE

MIDNIGHT DREARY
     BURNED SHALL BE LIFTED SLOWLY CREEPING 
BIRD OR FIEND
     THRILLED ME
AND MY SOUL NOTHING MORE,

FIERY EYES
     NEVER FLITTING
QUOTH THE RAVEN NOTHING MORE 

THRILLED ME FIERY EYES
     THRILLED ME
DARKNESS THERE
     SLOWLY CREEPING

     NOTHING MORE

QUOTH THE RAVEN NOTHING MORE

     STILL SITTING.... SHALL BE LIFTED
     NOTHING MORE

     THRILLED ME DARKNESS THERE SLOWLY CREEPING

     YET AGAIN

     NEVERMORE
